snippet.title: Hard Time III (Remix)
snippet.description:
This remixed trailer may include a fistful of content you've never witnessed before - not least the AI-generated rap courtesy of @entrophyer?! 

The game has escaped onto ALL platforms, so hunt it down now:
https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/hard-time-iii-switch
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3009850/Hard_Time_III
https://apps.apple.com/app/hard-time-iii/id6502045884
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MDickie.HardTimeIII
